# shadcn UI

This project uses [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/) for all UI elements.

## Configuration

shadcn is configured in [components.json](mdc:components.json) with:

- **Style:** new-york
- **RSC:** enabled
- **Icon library:** lucide
- **CSS variables:** enabled
- **Base color:** neutral

## Component Aliases

- UI components: `@/components/ui`
- General components: `@/components`
- Utilities: `@/lib/utils`
- Hooks: `@/hooks`

## Rules

- Always use shadcn UI components instead of building custom UI primitives.
- If shadcn is not initialized, run: `npx shadcn@latest init`
- If a required component is not yet installed, add it with: `npx shadcn@latest add <component>`
  - Example: `npx shadcn@latest add button`
- Import UI components from `@/components/ui/<component>`.
- Use the `cn()` utility from `@/lib/utils` for conditional class merging.
